dct_title_s: Fresno to General Grant National Park, Hume, and Kings River Canyon
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, and text (grade percentage).
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, various facilities, road quality.
Indicates distances from Fresno and General Grant National Park.
Includes "Note" text concerning motorists entering the park.
Numbered 204 in lower corners and 47 in left margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
